gokarna is a 2003 kannada film starring superstar upendra and rakshita . the film was directed by naganna and was upendra 's home production , made under his banner of anegudda vinayaka productions . music for the film was scored by gurukiran . it is the second among a series of successful films under upendra - naganna combination . the film also starred madhu bangarappa , tennis krishna , s.ramesh , satyajit , dr.nagesh , and indhudhar in supporting roles . the film is a remake of the 1992 tamil film annamalai starring rajinikanth